{"tid":2314832,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE人到現場「MAMA只拿兩獎」　錯失大賞、女團獎⋯深夜網戰翻！","createTime":"2020-12-06T20:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T10:40:01.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3bbf313eca9661118ab0de8e7c372ac0ec2c52f6","tid":2314832,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:15:35.000Z","msg":"2020年MAMA頒獎典禮（Mnet Asian Music Awards）6日在南韓舉辦，因疫情關係以無觀眾方式進行。南韓女團TWICE拿下「最受歡迎藝人」和「Worldwide Fans' Choice」兩獎，但她們曾經是大賞「年度歌曲」三連霸的歌手，也拿過三次「最佳女團」獎，今年的成績引起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5317/d5317973.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5317%2Fd5317973.jpg&h=82500ca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE出席2020年MAMA頒獎典禮。（圖／Curtesy of CJ ENM提供）<br />\n<br />\nTWICE過去得過三次「最佳女團」，更有連續三年拿下「最佳舞蹈表演女團」的紀錄，不少粉絲看好她們會繼續蟬聯。而照慣例，歷年來有到場的歌手，獲獎的機率比較高，不過最終上述兩獎都由不克出席的BLACKPINK獲獎，打斷TWICE連霸紀錄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5318/d5318241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5318%2Fd5318241.jpg&h=54620bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE「九缺一」出席2020年MAMA頒獎典禮。（圖／Curtesy of CJ ENM提供）<br />\n<br />\n比起過去抱獎連連，最後也只奪下「最受歡迎藝人」和共有10組藝人拿到的「Worldwide Fans' Choice」，讓粉絲抱不平更覺得疑惑。典禮結束後，「TWICE沒拿到獎」上了大陸微博熱搜，儘管大部分粉絲皆表示「明年再接再厲」，但也有激烈的TWICE和BLACKPINK，雙方各自護主吵了起來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5318/d5318240.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5318%2Fd5318240.jpg&h=98c80b65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「TWICE沒拿到獎」登上大陸微博熱搜。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n至於韓網，TWICE也同樣引起熱議，卻不是因為獎項。由於成員定延因為心理健康問題暫時休息中，並未出席典禮，但她的歌聲依舊出現在TWICE首次演出的新歌《CRY FOR ME》舞台中。或許是粉絲太想念定延，或是觀看典禮的觀眾疑惑她為何沒有現身，讓「TWICE定延活動中斷」登上了韓網熱門關鍵字。<br />\n<br />\n▲TWICE在2020年MAMA頒獎典禮拿下兩獎。（圖／Curtesy of CJ ENM提供）<br />\n<br />\nMAMA 2020完整得獎名單：防彈少年團狂掃8獎成最大贏家！<br />\n<br />\nMAMA致敬BTS貢獻⋯照片卻「只放六個人」 粉絲傻眼：超沒誠意！<br />\n<br />\nMAMA／IZ*ONE爆「兩人造假」首回歸 宮脇咲良站C位⋯粉絲心疼應援"},{"pid":"3a5a7f0301d9884c54801e4a9b49a42f49ef6245","tid":2314832,"uid":128127,"like":74,"dislike":9,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T20:46:30.000Z","msg":"唱好自己啲歌先再講拎唔拎到獎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QhcEbbAn2EY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQhcEbbAn2EY&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2hjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=7fb3a51a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QhcEbbAn2EY</a>"},{"pid":"3f1d08a02cef4c2bdb4a5d4340c0c521bfed5e71","tid":2314832,"uid":112747,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T21:02:02.000Z","msg":"佢地今年d歌都好普通"},{"pid":"26e42d2e9161ee66ac59da55612c730605763c7c","tid":2314832,"uid":40272,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:28:29.000Z","msg":"做愛無新花款 老闆唔喜歡"},{"pid":"31087a9fb3f2672c63c3d09661029bb3a44a17d1","tid":2314832,"uid":335866,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:28:42.000Z","msg":"我想問下今時今日佢地做live仲喺唔喺咪嘴？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97e00e6197bc167181810f1f601bc6d4f02e991","tid":2314832,"uid":335866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31087a9fb3f2672c63c3d09661029bb3a44a17d1","tid":2314832,"uid":335866,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:28:42.000Z","msg":"我想問下今時今日佢地做live仲喺唔喺咪嘴？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:29:47.000Z","msg":"我講緊d韓團"},{"pid":"f5befbcc5a700338c204d54a0a4c04f47b4a25fe","tid":2314832,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:32:54.000Z","msg":"分d比其他人拎囉無咩所謂<br />\n反正拎咗咁多年"},{"pid":"060fbc4b050ef44cc687714702e29b333b71c9c1","tid":2314832,"uid":47311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T00:33:48.000Z","msg":"MAMA 是但啦<br />\n人人都有分<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=